These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-1::.
4 different pets are kept: ferret, rat, mouse, horse
1. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
2. the owner of the rat is somewhere between the owner of the mouse and the owner of the horse##7
3. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Pet   | mouse | rat | horse | ferret |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-2::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, kiwi, onion, corn
1. the person eating onion is on the right of the person eating corn##1
2. the person eating onion is somewhere between the person eating kiwi and the person eating avocado##7
3. the person eating onion is between the person eating kiwi and the person eating corn##2

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food   | avocado | corn | onion | kiwi |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-3::.
There 4 different types of food: onion, cauliflower, artichoke, broccoli
1. the person eating onion is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
2. the person eating broccoli is somewhere between the person eating artichoke and the person eating cauliflower##7
3. the person eating artichoke is somewhere to the right of the person eating broccoli##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |  2   |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | onion | cauliflower | broccoli | artichoke |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, skateboard, ship, helicopter
1. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere between the person driving the ship and the person driving the skateboard##7
2. the person driving the van is somewhere to the left of the person driving the helicopter##5
3. the person driving the van is between the person driving the helicopter and the person driving the ship##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |   3   |    4    |
| Transport   | ship | van | helicopter | skateboard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, adventure, western, fantasy
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the person watching adventure movies is between the person watching time-travel movies and the person watching fantasy movies##2
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
4. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere between the person watching western movies and the person watching fantasy movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |   3   |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | western | time-travel | adventure | fantasy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, argentine, dutch, american
1. the malaysian is somewhere between the american and the argentine##7
2. the dutch is somewhere between the malaysian and the american##7
3. the dutch is on the left or right of the american##3
4. the dutch is somewhere to the right of the american##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |     3     |    4    |
| Nationality   | american | dutch | malaysian | argentine |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-7::.
