1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking mirinda##7
2. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking sprite##7
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |    2     |   3   |      4      |
| Beverage   | mirinda | hot-chocolate | soy-milk | sprite |

